<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>6333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从前，一个富人和他的儿子生活在一个小村庄里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这位父亲不得不送他的儿子到很远的地方去上学。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“儿子。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会在这所学校受到良好的教育。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他的儿子远离家乡去上学了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>父亲很伤心。但他相信一切都值得。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的儿子总有一天会成为一个成功并学有所成的人回到家乡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几年后，这位父亲的身体变得非常虚弱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他叫来了仆人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“过来。我要你记下我的遗愿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可能再也见不到我的儿子了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，主人。”仆人答应道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对于你，我的仆人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我将会给你所有的金钱和土地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对于我的儿子，我只会留给他一件东西，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他可以任意选择他想要的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请把我的遗愿传达给我的儿子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，主人。”仆人答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久这位父亲去世了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！他所有的一切都是我的了。”仆人大笑道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他十分高兴地跑到小主人跟前，并转达了他父亲的遗嘱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！爸爸！”儿子哭道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一段时间过去了，这个儿子悲伤而困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不明白为什么父亲把所有的东西都留给了仆人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>却只满足自己一个要求。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么父亲把一切都留给仆人？为什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个儿子向他充满智慧的老师求教。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老师，我从没有伤害过父亲，并且一直努力听他的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我以为他很爱我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但现在我一点儿都不这么觉得了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请不要这么想。”老师回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他真是一位有智慧的父亲！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？我不明白。”儿子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老师解释道，“你说过你父亲死时，只有那位仆人在家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”儿子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么，万一他死后，这个仆人卷走他所有的钱财怎么办？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你的父亲一定是担心这件事儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以他告诉仆人一切都将属于他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样，这个仆人才乐意过来告诉你你父亲的死讯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是这对我有什么好处？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人现在占有了一切！”儿子埋怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好好想想这件事儿。”老师建议道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“记住，仆人的一切财产都属于他的主人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你父亲不是说你可以要求得到一样东西吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么要求你父亲的仆人做你的仆人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样你父亲的一切都会属于你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”儿子哭了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在理解我的父亲了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我必须马上赶回家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他谢过老师后离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他回到家后，他见到了父亲的仆人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来这儿要提出我的要求。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的。”仆人答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“根据你父亲的遗嘱，你只能要求得到一样东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我唯一的要求是你用余生服侍我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？没门儿！”这个仆人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是在仆人内心深处，他明白自己的一切财富都属于主人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他没法拒绝这个要求。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要悲伤。”儿子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会和你分享我的财富。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，谢谢！我很高兴为你服务！”仆人答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个儿子很自豪自己是这么有智慧的父亲的儿子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他努力使自己成为父亲那样的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对自己的仆人非常好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最终，这个儿子也成为了一个有智慧并且很成功的商人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像他的父亲一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>